Articles.Content:
Oi peeps, me again! Im currently working on releasing my universe story thing. Stay tuned!

A sneak peak so far:

https://www.wattpad.com/402424301-welcome-to-iconel-anno-2536-what-is-iconel

Or read it here:

Spoiler

Iconel is a future empire, that expands throughout the Orion Arm. Not only is it the biggest and most peaceful civilization, its also the first, founded by humans in approximately 2150 AD. Iconel  also is the base of other seperate interstellar states, like the Robotics Republic of the Orion Arm, because the Iconel people created the Robots. Iconel is so big and massive that its name litterly means Iconic. The Iconel Empire is a system full of diverse cultures and species too. But there is still much more to this...

What do you peeps think?
